data.description: Warmth, Style, and Welcoming are a few descriptions of this Ridgewood S/D home!   This 3 bdrm 2 bth beauty is close to Harps grocery story and not far from Westside Elementary School.  Open living, dining & kitchen floor plan also split floor plan with the master apart from the two spare bedrooms.  Wood and tile floors throughout with granite in kitchen and bathrooms.  Master bath has jacuzzi tub with shower & walk in closet. Double garage offers extra storage and the deck in the backyard overlooks a firepit for those cool nights to roast those hot dogs or marshmallows!  The backyard is full of raised beds where the seller has raised vegetables and lots of herbs they can convey with the property.  This home would make a wonderful starter home or for those empty nesters wanting to simplify!  Call for your tour of this beauty today!
